OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FA 61-year-old man from Birmingham has
OL,8,Fbeen sentenced to an indefinite
OL,9,Fhospital order after stalking TV and
OL,10,Fradio star Myleene Klass by posting
OL,11,Fher an air pistol, handcuffs, a police
OL,12,Funiform and "disturbing" unwanted
OL,13,Fletters.
OL,15,FPeter Windsor was also convicted of
OL,16,Fstalking Klass's Classic FM colleague
OL,17,FKatie Breathwick by sending her
OL,18,Fdetails of a DIY will-writing kit and
OL,19,Fother "raving" and "unhinged" mail.
OL,26,@tD@MOUtD@XO]{D@GOU{D@NO]{D@TOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
