FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FMyleene Klass previously told the
OL,8,Fcourt how she felt "sheer terror"
OL,9,Fafter being sent items by Windsor, who
OL,10,Fhas been diagnosed with schizophrenia
OL,11,Fand claimed to be not guilty by reason
OL,12,Fof insanity.
OL,14,FWindsor, of Mary Road in Stechford,
OL,15,Fhad denied stalking both Klass and
OL,16,FBreathwick by sending items to Classic
OL,17,FFM's central London studios between
OL,18,FMarch 2020 and August 2024.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
