PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FNeither Klass nor Breathwick attended
OL,8,FCoventry Crown Court on Thursday as
OL,9,FWindsor, of Mary Road, Stechford,
OL,10,FBirmingham, was given a hospital order
OL,11,Fand a restraining order preventing him
OL,12,Ffrom contacting them until further
OL,13,Forder.
OL,15,FIn her evidence to the court,
OL,16,FBreathwick told jurors she was left
OL,17,Fterrified by Windsor, who also sent
OL,18,Fher numerous hand-written notes,
OL,19,Fbinoculars, perfume and running shoes.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FShe told the trial that she informed
OL,8,FKlass of around 100 notes and gifts
OL,9,Fbecause she felt her colleague needed
OL,10,Fto be aware of a situation that might
OL,11,Fput her at risk.
OL,13,FWindsor sent a note calling Klass a
OL,14,F"naughty vixen", and mailed Breathwick
OL,15,Fa letter saying he wanted to go
OL,16,Fpaddling in a lake with both women
OL,17,Fwhile drinking champagne, the court
OL,18,Fheard.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
