PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FBoth complainants became upset during
OL,8,Fthe evidence, with Klass telling the
OL,9,Fcourt how Royal Mail had found an air
OL,10,Fpistol addressed to her.
OL,12,FPassing sentence, Judge Tom Rochford
OL,13,Fsaid: "What you did caused both women
OL,14,Fconsiderable harm, fear and distress.
OL,15,FBoth were visibly and obviously
OL,16,Fdistressed when they gave their
OL,17,Fevidence.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
