CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,F"I accept you suffer from paranoid
OL,8,Fschizophrenia and have very serious
OL,9,Fissues with your mental health. They
OL,10,Fare at the centre of your offending.
OL,12,F"Each message or item you sent was
OL,13,Fdeliberate. You were on an upward or
OL,14,Fworsening trajectory.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
