PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FThe judge said he was satisfied it was
OL,8,Fhis schizophrenia in a "very large
OL,9,Fmeasure" that had been what caused him
OL,10,Fto commit offences, and concluded that
OL,11,F"the most appropriate way of dealing
OL,12,Fwith (him) is to make a hospital
OL,13,Forder."
OL,15,FThe 47-year-old former Hear'Say singer
OL,16,Fsaid "it just felt extreme on every
OL,17,Ffront" after she was informed in
OL,18,FAugust last year by her employer's
OL,19,Fsecurity staff about packages sent by
OL,20,FWindsor.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@HO]sD@AOUuD@GO]xD@FOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
