CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FInvited to describe her feelings when
OL,8,Fshe was informed by a police constable
OL,9,Fin September last year that an air gun
OL,10,Fhad been intercepted, Ms Klass told
OL,11,Fthe court: "He said to me that whilst
OL,12,Fthe gun wasn't necessary for a licence
OL,13,Fin this country, at such close
OL,14,Fproximity right up to 6ft it could
OL,15,Fprove fatal and police took it very
OL,16,Fseriously.
OL,18,F"I was extremely shocked because
OL,19,Fsuddenly it felt extremely real. It's
OL,20,Fa gun in a box with my name on it."
OL,26,@sD@LOUzD@AOU|D@cO]
