PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FIn an interview with ITV News in
OL,8,FOctober, Myleene Klass spoke about the
OL,9,Fimpact of being stalked, explaining
OL,10,Fthat she didn't know who she had to be
OL,11,Fscared of
OL,13,FWhat to do if you are being stalked
OL,15,FWest Midlands Police said they would
OL,16,Fencourage anyone who thinks they are
OL,17,Fbeing stalked to report it to police
OL,18,Fstraightaway, if you are in immediate
OL,19,Fdanger call 999, otherwise you can
OL,20,Freport online using their Live Chat or
OL,21,Fby calling 101.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
