OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773943560
OL,3,CStalker who posted air gun and
OL,4,Chandcuffs to radio host Myleene Klass
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FIf you are not ready to speak to
OL,8,Fpolice, reach out for support from the
OL,9,FWest Midlands Stalking Support
OL,10,FService, which offers support for
OL,11,Fwomen and men affected by stalking
OL,12,Facross the West Midlands. Their 24
OL,13,Fhour helpline is 0121 552 6447.
OL,15,FAlternatively, visit the
OL,16,Fblackcountrywomensaid.co.uk website or
OL,17,Fthe National Stalking Helpline.
OL,19,FOfficers also encourage people to keep
OL,20,Fa record of events, such as:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
