OL,7,F Note details of any witnesses
OL,9,F Keep a record of text messages,
OL,10,Fcalls, voicemails, or social media
OL,11,Fcontact etc
OL,13,F Keep a diary of events, noting down
OL,14,Fdates, times, locations and any other
OL,15,Fdetails to describe what has happened
